\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 In England they used to have to sit in silence in the old days.
