\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Before you started and - and - and when you finished. Every meal.
