\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 There were some you could buy from a shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Oh yes, there was a shop - oh in the shops, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Could you ever bring a book to the table or a toy at a mealtime?
