 we were - un - unless - indeed there wasn't much distinction here in Barra I must - can't say that. Of course a young - boy that left here, he was often just like ourselves with poor parents, he went away to see and did well for himself, went up and got 
his master's ticket, well he used to come home you know, and oh he was - and everybody was - looking up to him.
\par 
