\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 No, he'd - talk to you the same as he - used to - usually did. Mm hm.
