ck used to come over to Bentangval. There was no way of keeping them out. But he came one time - suggested that he should fence Bentangval off - from the shore here right down to the west side, that cut - they were able to keep their own all their own, an
d Bentangval in. And he approached Lady Gordon Cathcart for a - the - to help the crofters to get this done, fenced. A}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3623188\charrsid1072312 nd - he did. She gave them the m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
