r person, what are they meaning in their minds, what are they thinking if they say that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Think that she was a very sort of quality.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Good quality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Not money or position?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 No, no. Kind, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 So it can mean any person, it doesn't have to be a person of money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 
You were saying how a person might become an MA and come back and people would look up to him a bit, but were there any families among the crofters and fishermen who felt themselves to be a bit superior to others do you think, or were thought to be?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Well not to any great - not - no, no, really no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Were there any families that were thought to be not very good or a bit bad or rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Oh well, yes, there was the odd - the odd - family that didn't - weren't as cheery as some.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 With drinking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 
