\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Ah they were - were all the same really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 
I was wondering if there was a family perhaps where there was a lot of drinking if it would make a big difference to the way the children were dressed and fed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 It would - I suppose it would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 You don't remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Don't remember very well no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 It wasn't a problem here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 I think it was probably more in cities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Yes. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 I think a lot of people were brought up at that time to fear drink and what it could do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Mm hm. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 It didn't come in here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 
I remember asking about your father's job, did he ever do anything else besides the jobs you told me, the herring fishing and labouring on the mainland in the winter? Did he ever have any other paid work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 That was his life's work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 That was his way - way he lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4155104 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 At the table, could you ask for a second helping if you wanted more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3027436 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775577\charrsid1072312 Oh yes, oh yes, oh yes.
